description: Number of n-step self-avoiding paths on quadrant grid starting at quadrant origin.
references: A. J. Guttmann and G. M. Torrie, Critical behavior at an edge for the SAW and Ising model, J. Phys. A 17 (1984), 3539-3552. See series coefficients c_{n}^{2} for square lattice with wedge angle Pi/2.
author: _David W. Wilson_
